data.value:
Dutch Mill Delight is a probiotic drink that contains duo active combination of Pro and Prebiotic fiber. Prebiotic fiber is a plant fiber that helps nourish good live bacteria inside the tummy. When probiotic and prebiotic are combined, it produces longer living good bacteria which makes tummy better and absorbs nutrients faster.
Type of Milk: Probiotic drink with prebiotic fiber
Ideal For:
Individuals aiming to improve digestion Maintaining a healthy gut flora Children and adults looking for a tasty, nutritious drink
Ingredients:
Water Sugar Milk solids Lactobacillus casei (probiotic) Prebiotic fiber Flavoring
Storage: Keep refrigerated at 2–8°C. Consume before the indicated expiry date.
Where to buy: Robinsons Supermarkets Makati, SM Seaside Cebu
______________________________________________________________________________
Nutrition Facts (Per 100ml)
Energy: 80 kcal
Protein: 1g
Carbohydrates: 18g
Fat: 0g
Dietary Fiber: 1g
Probiotic Content: Billions of live Lactobacillus casei
